1 AN ACT concerning
2 Health Facilities – Delegation of Inspection Authority Augmentation of Survey
3 Staff – Nursing Homes
4 FOR the purpose of requiring the Secretary of Health, on request of a county, to delegate
5 to the county the authority to conduct site visits and full surveys of nursing homes;
6 requiring that the Maryland Department of Health and certain counties equally
7 share certain costs under certain circumstances augment State nursing home survey
8 staff using county funds under certain circumstances; requiring the Maryland
9 Department of Health to initiate a certain memorandum of understanding and
10 develop a certain plan with a requesting county within a certain period of time; and
11 generally relating to the inspection of nursing homes and the delegation of authority.
